I\'92m so much happier now that I\'92m dead.\
\
Technically, missing. Soon to be presumed dead. But as shorthand, we\'92ll say dead. It\'92s been only a matter of hours, but I feel better already: loose joints, wavy muscles. At one point this morning, I realized my face felt strange, different. I looked in the rearview mirror \'96 dread Carthage forty-three miles behind me, my smug husband lounging around his sticky bar as mayhem dangled on a thin piano wire just above his shitty, oblivious head \'96 and I realized I was smiling. Ha! That\'92s new.\
